			h1
				img(src="img/logo.svg", alt="Brackets Logo")
				| Brackets
			.hero
				h2 Contribute!
				img(src="img/brackets-abstract.svg", alt="Brackets")
				section
					h3 Let's Build Awesome, Together
					p Brackets is an open source code editor built in HTML, CSS, and JavaScript.  It is designed from the ground up to make it easy for web developers, like you, to hack on it and to write extensions.
					p We’ve rounded up all the information you’ll need to get started and organized it on this handy site.
		#content
			section#getting-started
				h2 Getting Started
				article.source
					h3 Get the Source
					p So to start, you'll need Brackets, and you can find it on Github. Take a look a the code, fork it, pull a clone, whatever you want.
					p New to Git and Github? You can get started with github:help.
				article.tutorials
					h3 Tutorials
					ul
						li: a(href="#") How to Hack on Brackets
						li: a(href="#") How to Write Extensions
						li: a(href="#") Brackets Extensions
						li: a(href="#") Simple "Hello World" extension
					p Writing your own Brackets tutorials? Let us know.
				article.videos
					h3 Video Presentations
					iframe.video(width="360", height="155", src="http://www.youtube.com/embed/xirIHMtpc4c?list=PL69EAABFC3B569526&amp;hl=en_US", frameborder="0", allowfullscreen)
